            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Debit the relevant expense and credit an accrued liability account at the reporting date. Electricity of Rs 80,000 consumed in March but billed in April is recorded as Debit Power and Fuel Rs 80,000, Credit Accrued Expenses Rs 80,000. When the bill arrives the accrual is reversed and the supplier invoice is booked normally."
